\c 13
\s Munyengetero wekukumbira rubatsiro
\d Kumutungamiriri wekuimba. Pisarema raDhavhidhi.
\p
\v 1 Kusvika rinhi Jehovha muchindikanganwa\x + Map. 79.5. 89.46.\x* nekusingaperi\x + Map. 79.5. 89.46.\x*? Kusvika rinhi muchindivanzira chiso chenyu\x + Job. 13.24. Map. 89.46.\x*?
\v 2 Kusvika rinhi ndichiisa mazano mumweya wangu, kusuruvara mumoyo mangu nezuva? Kusvika rinhi muvengi wangu achikwiridzirwa pamusoro pangu?
\v 3 Tarirai, ndipindurei, Jehovha Mwari wangu; vhenekerai meso angu\x + Ezi. 9.8. Map. 19.8. 1 Sam. 14.27.\x*, zvimwe ndirare hope dzerufu\x + Jer. 51.39.\x*;
\v 4 zvimwe muvengi wangu ati: Ndamukunda\x + Map. 25.2. 30.1. 35.19,24. 38.16.\x*; vadzivisi vangu vafare kana ndazununguka\x + Map. 10.6.\x*.
\v 5 Asi ini ndakavimba munyasha yenyu\x + Map. 28.7. 33.21. Map. 25.2.\x*; moyo wangu uchafara muruponeso rwenyu\x + Map. 28.7. 33.21. Map. 25.2.\x*\x + Map. 9.14.\x*.
\v 6 Ndichaimbira Jehovha, nokuti wakandiitira zvakanaka kwazvo\x + Map. 103.10. 116.7. 119.17. 142.7.\x*.